 great about…and that everyone will enjoy looking to turn that music into learning strike a chord with family tambourine making launch the station what makes bright horizons a unique place to learn come visit our center to find out our caring staff and expert educators are here to answer all of your questions  about safety individualized curriculum teacher training learning environments and more with a tour you can feel sure the center is right for your child so you can make your choice with confidenceschedule your tour of all of our unique indoor and outdoor learning environments today come visit us  reasons to visit us contact us to schedule a visit  passionate  caring teachers  curriculum in action see the other  reasons   about the curriculum our unique approach to education bright horizons’ the world at their fingertips children learn in a variety of ways and at their own pace our carefully planned curriculum is designed to inspire your child at every age and stage built around extensive research stcentury technology and developmentally appropriate instruction our curriculum introduces concepts of math science language culture environment art and health more about our teachers helping children reach their potential our teachers inspired by knowledgeable child development professionals who understand the balance between nurturing developing minds and caring for tender spirits children grow from curious infants into explorative preschoolers our teachers are all experienced and highly trained meeting rigid certification requirements they keep up with the latest techniques in early childhood curriculum and continually develop new skills to guide children on a path to lifelong learning read more health  safety because parents need peace of mind well aware and staying healthy our center environment offers children a healthy and safe place to develop and learn through our well aware program and our staying healthy procedures we set high expectations for creating healthy environments and also foster positive attitudes within children towards healthy living physical activity and nutrition we’re proud to provide programs parents can feel good about and to be recognized as a model for other early education programs by the partnership for a healthier america and first lady michelle obama’s let’s move campaign read more test welcome to the bright horizons family yelp yelp sorry you’re not allowed to access this page contact yelp if you keep experiencing issues cupertino daycare  preschool  bright horizons at cupertino corporate careers efamily news photo gallery get directions from go print from s take the wolfe rd exit and turn right onto wolfe rd from n take the wolfe rd exit and turn left onto wolfe rd from s exit  south towards cupertino exit onto s and exit on wolfe rd from n exit moffett blvd toward mountain view merge onto s exit  south towards cupertino exit onto s and take wolfe rd exit once on wolfe rd vallco shopping center will be on your right hand side turn right onto stevens creek blvd sears will be on corner turn right on north portal ave chuck e cheese is on the corner the center will be on the lefthand side after portal park turn left into parking lot the center is a brick building at the end of the parking lot right next to portal park bright horizons at cupertino home » usa » ca » cupertino » bright horizons at cupertino cupertino child care center address  north portal ave cupertino ca  call for enrollment information  phone  hours of operation mf  am to  pm ages served infants toddlers preschool kindergarten prep map it find another location schedule a visit tell us a bit about yourself to get started number of children expecting       when would you like to start within a month  months  months  months  months unsure at this time what time would you like to visit am – pm pm – pm pm – pm yes please send me efamily news for weekly parenting tips strategies and resources from early education experts submit continue 